These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | board-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, car
1. the person driving the car is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Transport   | subway | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat
1. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Cigar   | fonseca | baccarat |

